com.netease.cloud.client

接口 StreamProxy

  • 所有已知实现类:
    StreamProxyClient

    public interface StreamProxy
    The interface for accessing the Netease streamproxy service. Netease streamproxy provides storage service on the Internet. This streamproxy Java SDK provides a simple interface that can be used to store and retrieve any amount of data, at any time, from anywhere on the web.
